1.3 o que é o lakeflow do databricks?
é uma unified plataform for data ingestion, transformation and orchestration.

1.4 quais os componentes do lakeflow?
lakeflow connect, lakeflow declarative pipelines, lakeflow jobs

1.5 o que é lakeflow connect?
a set of efficient ingestion connectors that simplify data ingestion from popular enterprise applications, databases, cloud storage, message buses, and local files

1.6 o que é lakeflow declarative pipelines?
a framework for building batch and streaming data pipelines using sql and python, designed to accelerate etl development

1.7 o que é lakeflow jobs?
a workflow automation tool for databricks that orchestrates data processing workloads. It enables coordination of multiple tasks within complex workflows, allowing for the scheduling, optimization, and management of repeatable processes.

