a managed and efficient solution that reduces costs and accelarates time to value, self-service interfaces that enable practitioner across the organization to easily ingest data from enterprise application, unified obsevability and governance to ensure secure, reliable, and well-monitored pipelines and tables.

1.9 quais os 3 tipos de conectores de ingestao que o lakeflow connect da suporte?
manual file uploads, standard connectors(cloud object storage, Kafka), managed connectors(from enterprise applications (SaaS, databases))

1.10 quais os tipos de ingestao do lakeflow connect?
batch - load data as batches of rows into databricks, often based on a schedule
incremental batch - only new data is ingested, previoly loaded records are skipped automatically
streaming - continuosly load data rows or batches of data rows as it is generated so you can query it as it arrives in near real-time 
