1.14 quais sao as key features do delta lake?
ACID transactions, data manipulation language, time travel, schema evolution and enforcement

1.15 o que é ACID in delta lake?
ACID transactions  (Atomicity, Consistency, Isolation, and Durability) for all operation, allowing multiple users to read and write data concurretly without conflicts.

1.16 qual é o suporte do delta lake para DML?
